```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Formation: Strategic Outcome Identified

    Formation --> Active: Product Triad Assembled<br/>Pool Resources Allocated<br/>RFC Approved

    state Formation {
        [*] --> OutcomeDefinition: Portfolio Pool
        OutcomeDefinition --> TriadSelection: PMO Pool
        TriadSelection --> CapabilityRequest: Product Triad
        CapabilityRequest --> GovernanceReview: Resource Match
        GovernanceReview --> [*]: Approval
    }

    state Active {
        [*] --> Delivery
        Delivery --> Retrospective: Biweekly
        Retrospective --> Delivery: Improvements Applied
        Delivery --> StakeholderReview: Weekly
        StakeholderReview --> Delivery: Feedback
        Delivery --> GovernanceCheckpoint: Monthly
        GovernanceCheckpoint --> Delivery: Alignment Confirmed
    }

    Active --> OutcomeAchieved: Success Criteria Met
    Active --> Blocked: Critical Blocker

    Blocked --> Active: Blocker Resolved
    Blocked --> Pivot: Strategic Shift Required

    OutcomeAchieved --> Dissolve: One-Time Outcome
    OutcomeAchieved --> Pivot: New Related Outcome
    OutcomeAchieved --> Sustain: Ongoing Support Needed

    state Dissolve {
        [*] --> KnowledgeCapture
        KnowledgeCapture --> ResourceReturn: Publish RFC/ADR<br/>Update Playbooks
        ResourceReturn --> [*]: Triad to Pool/New Squad
    }

    state Pivot {
        [*] --> NewOutcome: Redefine Mission
        NewOutcome --> [*]: Return to Active
    }

    state Sustain {
        [*] --> MaintenanceMode: Reduce Capacity<br/>Automate Operations
        MaintenanceMode --> [*]: Operational Team Takes Over
    }

    Dissolve --> [*]
    Pivot --> Active
    Sustain --> [*]

    note right of Formation
        Duration: 1-2 weeks
        Governance: RFC review
        Output: Squad charter
    end note

    note right of Active
        Duration: Varies (4-16 weeks typical)
        Rhythm: Daily standups, weekly reviews
        Metrics: Outcome progress, quality, velocity
    end note

    note right of OutcomeAchieved
        Criteria: Success metrics met
        Documentation: Lessons learned
        Handoff: Knowledge transfer
    end note
```
